==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bielas comet
<hw>Bie"la's com"et</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>A
periodic comet, discovered by Biela in 1826, which revolves around the
sun in 6.6 years. The November meteors (Andromedes or Bielids) move in
its orbit, and may be fragments of the comet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

